snippet.title: Quake Maps - Bestial Devastation
snippet.description:
Custom Quake Map: Bestial Devastation
Author: John "DaMaul" McCann
Year: 1999

Download: https://www.quaddicted.com/reviews/damaul6.html
Zerstörer mod (& game): https://www.quaddicted.com/reviews/zer.html

A great, large industrial level with interesting Zerstörer additions
(I added a high definition skybox for a little visual "pop").

This video uses the updated "Alternate Quake Music" pack at the end, to avoid
copyright claim garbage. You can get it here: http://www.quaketastic.com/files/music/aqm2_pack.zip
